text.section:
Permits issued by the Department under the following sections shall be issued in accordance with this subtitle:
Air quality control permits to construct subject to § 2-404 of this article;
Permits to install, materially alter or materially extend landfill systems, incinerators for public use or rubble landfills subject to § 9-209 of this article;
Permits to discharge pollutants to waters of the State issued pursuant to § 9-323 of this article;
Permits to install, materially alter or materially extend a structure used for storage or distribution of any type of sewage sludge issued, renewed, or amended pursuant to § 9-234.1 or § 9-238 of this article;
Permits to own, operate, establish or maintain a controlled hazardous substance facility issued pursuant to § 7-232 of this article;
Permits to own, operate, or maintain a hazardous material facility issued pursuant to § 7-103 of this article; and
Permits to own, operate, establish or maintain a low-level nuclear waste facility issued pursuant to § 7-233 of this article.
